metadata.name: You're my little aunt
metadata.description:
At this moment, Xiao Hong's voice again came from outside: "Master, are you ready? It's time to go to xia's house."



"All right, I'll be right out." Xiao Che took a look at his dress up at this time, ready to go out. Just take two steps, was xiao Ling xi hand hold, a serious face said: "small che! Before you go to marry Xia Jinyue, repeat the agreement we made yesterday. Not a word is allowed to be wrong, or you will not go out."



Yesterday's appointment? Xiao Che casually think, slightly helpless: "well... After getting married with summer month, can't have a wife and forget the little aunt, can't reduce the time with the little aunt, for the little aunt's call as before on call... Not a word
